Punch/Nemesis Enforcer/Scattershot:


Punch entered a CR chamber inside the Alliance base, cursing as he could feel 
mech-fluid dripping down his body.

----------


Nemesis Enforcer raised his rifle, firing off 10 rapid blasts from his 
rapid-fire laser rifle at Soundwave's abdomen.

Scattershot, along with the five autoguns present, opened fire, 6 armor 
piercing rounds flying at Soundwave's left knee.
